      <title>谢赫巴兹·谢里夫的哥哥下台，接任巴基斯坦最高职务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/shehbaz-sharif-set-pakistans-top-job-elder-brother-steps-aside-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谢巴兹·谢里夫将在未来几天内开始巴基斯坦总理的第二个任期，回到八月份上周选举前解散议会之前的职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/shehbaz-sharif-set-pakistans-top-job-elder-brother-steps-aside-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:56:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其埃尔多安十年来首次访问埃及，重点关注加沙</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/turkeys-erdogan-first-egypt-visit-decade-with-gaza-focus-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统塔伊普·埃尔多安周三自 2012 年以来首次访问埃及，会见总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西，为重建地区大国之间的关系迈出了一大步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/turkeys-erdogan-first-egypt-visit-decade-with-gaza-focus-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:51:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>柏林与在俄罗斯被拘留的德国人的律师取得联系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/berlin-contact-with-lawyers-detained-german-russia-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国外交部发言人周三表示，德国外交部已与一名抵达俄罗斯后被拘留的德国公民的律师取得联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/berlin-contact-with-lawyers-detained-german-russia-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世卫组织警告对加沙拉法的袭击将是一场“深不可测的灾难”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/who-warns-assault-gazas-rafah-would-be-an-unfathomable-catastrophe-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界卫生组织周三警告称，以色列对加沙南部拉法的军事进攻将造成“深不可测的灾难”，并将该飞地的卫生系统推向崩溃的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/who-warns-assault-gazas-rafah-would-be-an-unfathomable-catastrophe-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:31:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>古巴调香师用令人惊喜的成分制作本土香水</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/cuban-perfumist-makes-home-grown-fragrance-with-surprise-ingredient-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位古巴企业家相信她已经找到了一种独特的本土香水的配方，她希望有一天能够销往世界各地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/cuban-perfumist-makes-home-grown-fragrance-with-surprise-ingredient-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰加入联盟向乌克兰提供先进无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/netherlands-joins-coalition-supply-ukraine-with-advanced-drones-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰国防部长表示，荷兰正在与包括英国在内的盟友组成军事联盟，该联盟将为乌克兰提供先进的无人机技术，并增强其在针对俄罗斯的战争中的进攻能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/netherlands-joins-coalition-supply-ukraine-with-advanced-drones-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:05:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>解说：巴基斯坦债务危机有多严重，国际货币基金组织能否拯救？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-bad-is-pakistans-debt-crisis-can-imf-save-it-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦新政府的谈判缓解了上周选举结果未果后对该核武国家不稳定的直接担忧，但全面经济危机的风险仍然存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-bad-is-pakistans-debt-crisis-can-imf-save-it-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:02:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其山体滑坡后救援人员寻找失踪金矿工人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/rescue-workers-search-missing-gold-miners-after-turkey-landslide-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其内政部长表示，周三，土耳其东部一座金矿发生山体滑坡后，救援人员奋力寻找九名被困地下的工人，而官方媒体称，调查正在进行中，四人被拘留。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/rescue-workers-search-missing-gold-miners-after-turkey-landslide-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:57:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普建议放弃落后者后，北约主席表示美国需要盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-chief-says-18-countries-meet-2-military-spending-target-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约周三表示，欧洲增加了国防支出，美国需要盟友，几天前美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普暗示华盛顿可能不会保护支出不足的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-chief-says-18-countries-meet-2-military-spending-target-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利法官裁定联合国工作人员不得因刚果死亡事件受审</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italian-judge-rules-un-staffers-cannot-be-tried-over-congo-deaths-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名意大利法官裁定，联合国机构的两名雇员不能因 2021 年意大利驻刚果民主共和国大使、其保镖和一名司机的死亡而受到审判，因为他们拥有外交豁免权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/italian-judge-rules-un-staffers-cannot-be-tried-over-congo-deaths-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:13:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
